name: The Grimmo Reaper
description:
RANDOM EDITION N°1

There is no Banshee that doesn't love this Baimo

They guard all Baimos equally from danger, but appreciate how The Reaper is always at the forefront, accompanying them on their mission...



"The Grimmo Reaper is an event content, only obtainable by participating in the Battle Royale that will take place on the discord server. Join the battle, where only one Baimo will be victorious!"
